0of%20my%20early%20motherhood%20experiences%3B%20she%20shared%20current%20wisdom%20and%20things%20she%20had%20already%20learned%20about%20being%20a%20mom.%20We%20talked%20about%20how%20different%20parenting%20is%20in%20the%20age%20of%20Google%20and%20how%20much%20more%20society%20could%20do%20to%20make%20things%20easier%20for%20new%20moms.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20stumbled%20onto%20a%20universal%20truth%3A%20None%20of%20us%20really%20know%20what%20we're%20doing.%20Much%20of%20parenting%20is%20making%20things%20up%20as%20we%20go%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20daylong%20outings%20to%20the%20zoo%20and%20to%20a%20local%20flower%20farm.%20At%20times%2C%20I%20stepped%20back%20and%20watched.%20I%20stole%20moments%20to%20observe%20the%20rather%20ordinary%20transition%20of%20a%20new%20generation%20emerging.%20I%20marveled%20at%20my%20daughter's%20absolute%20competence%20and%20quiet%20confidence%20as%20she%20simply%20did%20what%20needed%20to%20be%20done.%20Had%20I%20been%20like%20that%3F%20Did%20she%20grasp%20these%20things%20intuitively%2C%20or%20had%20I%20somehow%2C%20unknowingly%2C%20passed%20on%20some%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsecrets%26quot%3B%20of%20motherhood%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1ebbe87-44a1-4aab-a15f-c868b20907df%5C%22%3EI%20cherish%20the%20time%20I%20spent%20with%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20knew%20it%2C%20our%20leaves%20were%20approaching%20their%20end.%20As%20anyone%20on%20the%20far%20side%20of%2030%20knows%2C%20time%20has%20a%20tendency%20to%20move%20much%20faster%20than%20we%20would%20like.%20While%20I%20was%20sad%20that%20she%20would%20soon%20be%20returning%20to%20work%2C%20I%20cherish%20the%20time%20we%20spent%20getting%20reacquainted%20as%20adults%20who%20are%20both%20called%20Mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20began%20as%20my%20attempt%20to%20make%20things%20easier%20for%20my%20daughter.%20It%20ended%20up%20strengthening%20what%20was%20already%20a%20close%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20long%20ago%20shifted%20to%20a%20