prises%20rely%20more%20and%20more%20on%20apps%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20lose%20track%20of%20who's%20using%20what%2C%20which%20can%20open%20the%20door%20to%20security%20risks.%20Reco's%20AI%20finds%20the%20apps%2C%20monitors%20how%20they're%20being%20used%2C%20and%20flags%20risks%20before%20they%20become%20big%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlein%20added%20that%20Reco%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20building%20AI%20agents%20that%20can%20quickly%20understand%20and%20fix%20app%20issues.%20The%20AI%20agents%20are%20trained%20on%20Reco%20metadata%20rather%20than%20customer%20data%2C%20making%20them%20faster%20and%20more%20secure%20than%20competitors%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20could%20foresee%20an%20AI%20revolution%2C%20and%20having%20thousands%20of%20AI%20applications%20is%20amazing%2C%20until%20you%20get%20to%20the%20problem%20of%2C%20'I'm%20a%20security%20expert%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20visibility'%2C%26quot%3B%20Klein%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20vision%20has%20been%20to%20empower%20teams%20and%20enable%20businesses%20so%20that%20security%20feels%20like%20innovation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReco%20is%20one%20of%20many%20startups%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20enterprise%20customers%20beef%20up%20their%20cybersecurity%20offerings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETel%20Aviv-based%20Torq%2C%20a%20no-code%20security%20platform%2C%20raised%20a%20%2470%20million%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20in%202024%20led%20by%20Evolution%20Equity%20Partners%20with%20participation%20from%20Bessemer%20Venture%20Partners.%207AI%2C%20which%20is%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Bswarm%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%20cybersecurity%20agents%2C%20launched%20from%20stealth%20in%202024%20with%20a%20%2436%20million%20seed%20round%20led%20by%20Greylock.%20And%20Astrix%20Security%2C%20which%20uses%20AI%20agents%20to%20shield%20enterprise%20customers%20from%20cyberattacks%2C%20raised%20a%20%2445%20million%20Series%20B%20in%202024%20led%20by%20Menlo%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdi