0little%20bit%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20heavy%20rain%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20cut%20off%20by%20rivers%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20So%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20in%20and%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sylvia%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20access%20was%20a%20challenge%20in%20itself.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20a%20riverbed%20for%2010%20kilometres%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sylvia%20says.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20could%20either%20walk%20it%20or%20go%20on%20a%20four-wheeler%2C%20a%20tractor%2C%20or%20a%20bike.%E2%80%9D%20On%20one%20occasion%2C%20their%20tractor%20lost%20balance%20and%20toppled%20over%20on%20the%20muddy%20track.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20bricks%20for%20the%20main%20house%20for%20the%20last%20two%20kilometres%20or%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20humour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelp%20from%20the%20local%20hands%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20homestay%20came%20to%20life%20not%20through%20contractors%20or%20architects%2C%20but%20through%20the%20hands%20of%20villagers%20from%20a%20tiny%20hamlet%20of%20just%20fifteen%20houses%20nearby.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20village%20kind%20of%20works%20as%20a%20community.%20They%20get%20together%20and%20build%20one%20person%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20and%20when%20the%20next%20person%20is%20building%2C%20everyone%20chips%20in%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccustomed%20to%20forest%20life%20and%20deeply%20skilled%20in%20traditional%20craftsmanship%20%E2%80%94%20from%20digging%20wells%20to%20carving%20wood%20%E2%80%94%20these%20villagers%20became%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20build.%20%E2%80%9CThey%E2%80%99re%20great%20at%20working%20in%20the%20forest%20and%20very%20strong.%20One%20or%20two%20masons%20will%20always%20be%20there%20in%20these%20interior%20villages%20because%20they%20build%20their%20own%20houses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sylvia%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E