iness%20is%20an%20enigma.%20He%20taps%20on%20this%20sentiment%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20you%20make%20your%20mind%20resilient%2C%20you%20can%20find%20happiness%20in%20every%20circumstance.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20believes%20tough%20times%20shape%20you%20and%20equip%20you%20well.%20%E2%80%9COur%20childhood%20in%20the%20villages%20was%20filled%20with%20us%20roaming%20the%20fields%2C%20eating%20wild%20sugarcane%2C%20and%20getting%20dirty%20in%20the%20mud.%20It%20made%20our%20body%20systems%20strong.%20This%20body%20is%20now%20helping%20me%20through%20life.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20his%20secret%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20reached%20this%20part%20of%20the%20story%20hoping%20to%20find%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20dietary%20secret%20behind%20his%20having%20no%20health%20complications%20at%2095%2C%20apologies.%20Sharma%20eats%20everything%20and%20enjoys%20a%20good%20burger%20as%20much%20as%20he%20does%20his%20%3Cem%3Eroti-sabji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20flatbread%20and%20vegetables).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20meals%20don%E2%80%99t%20include%20super-power%20rendering%20ingredients.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20Sharma%20focuses%20on%20the%20food%20he%20feeds%20his%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20surround%20yourself%20with%20wise%20people%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20not%20people%20the%20media%20shows%20as%20saints%2C%20but%20real%20wise%20people.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20interjects%20here%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F199661%2Fbengaluru-start-up-innovation-visually-challenged-technology-app-new%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20the%20smartphone%20has%20occupied%20our%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20activates%20our%20reward%20systems%2C%20creating%20a%20sort%20of%20ephemeral%20joy.%20So%2C%20does%20Sharma%20avoid%20the%20smartphone%20entirely%3F%20%E2%80%9CNo