s%2C%20which%20limits%20their%20effectiveness.%20%E2%80%9CEnsuring%20that%20all%20elements%20of%20a%20solar%20setup%20are%20provided%20is%20crucial%20for%20utility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20skilled%20youth%20should%20also%20be%20involved%20in%20deployment%20and%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Facilitating%20innovative%20energy%20solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReforms%20should%20also%20support%20innovative%20solar%20uses%20%E2%80%94%20like%20solar-powered%20tools%20and%20machinery%20for%20farmers%20and%20artisans%20%E2%80%94%20so%20that%20renewable%20energy%20can%20boost%20livelihoods.%20%E2%80%9CGovernment%20sponsorship%20for%20eco-friendly%20alternatives%20like%20solar%20stoves%2C%20which%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20significantly%2C%20can%20transform%20energy%20usage%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Tanveer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Support%20for%20new%20technologies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShani%20believes%20that%20clearer%20guidelines%20and%20faster%20certification%20processes%20should%20be%20put%20in%20place%20for%20innovative%20solar%20technologies%2C%20such%20as%20solar%20tiles%20and%20solar%20facades.%20Currently%2C%20these%20face%20long%20approval%20delays%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20standards.%20Streamlining%20the%20process%20would%20help%20new%20products%20enter%20the%20market%20more%20quickly%20and%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSolar-trees-shani-pandya-1-1737953689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5CnRecently%2C%20Shani%20met%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20showcased%20the%20innovative%20solar%20tile%20to%20him.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FSolar-trees-shani-pandya-1-1737953689.jpg%20